de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization

Class FixedStation

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization.FixedStation

  • public class FixedStation
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates a Fixed station object with getters and setters for all the parameters of a DatabaseHelper.fixedStationTable Table in Database. Used by FixedStationSync to create a new Fixed Station Object to be inserted into the Database.
    See Also:
    SyncActivity, FixedStationSync, de.awi.floenavigation.synchronization
